## ğŸŒ API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint        | Description             |
|--------|------------------|-------------------------|
| GET    | /api/books       | Get all books           |
| POST   | /api/books       | Add a new book          |
| PUT    | /api/books       | Update existing book    |
| DELETE | /api/books/{id}  | Delete book by ID       |

